{"tid":1183221,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日唔小心串親個健身狗","createTime":"2019-06-02T18:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T05:33:52.000Z","uid":7043,"like":146,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"01fb63f58ed9be8df4d8a7793bcac04ae6c8b49d","tid":1183221,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:15:05.000Z","msg":"話說今日係街行緊<br />\n有個男人拍我問我想唔想健身<br />\n以下係對話<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 健身狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n健身狗：有冇興趣試下健身呢？大隻d自信d又吸引囡囡多d<br />\n我：唔洗啦我條女唔鍾意男仔大隻<br />\n健身狗：你條女哄下你炸 好似男人個個都鍾意大波妹啦係咪 大隻d咪可以冧死佢囉<br />\n我：同你三唔識七我信你定信我條女呀？一陣大隻左條女飛左我係咪你俾你條女我屌呀？<br />\n<br />\n唔知佢係咪見我咁講嚇左嚇之後咁講<br />\n<br />\n健身狗：errrrrr 我冇女朋友<br />\n我：咁你仲話大隻d會吸引囡囡 你女都未溝到同我講呢d 下次溝到女施埋出黎咁sell我就信你啦 洗唔洗教呀<br />\n之後我就走左<br />\n依定諗返都唔明點解個陣會咁夠膽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286fd3c66d3f520dfcb1ab49887d204bdb3bb0fe","tid":1183221,"uid":157522,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:21:53.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"6cfcd7630452f80e98dab47d7aac0b6955f852a3","tid":1183221,"uid":29702,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:26:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc9ba22e4c60d28abdaa4999570b0c40957ff776","tid":1183221,"uid":38293,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:27:23.000Z","msg":"因為佢係gay"},{"pid":"f45d04716bdd1f78c85391a8733a960999be414d","tid":1183221,"uid":179967,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:30:00.000Z","msg":"講咁多托柒咩...達你連登個朵佢自然急急腳走架啦"},{"pid":"870b7d89753e4f3e2f12798aad19ae4be947821f","tid":1183221,"uid":51171,"like":5,"dislike":34,"score":-29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:39:08.000Z","msg":"d 表情符號打黎有咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70116cc2150b952cb1531164c98d3e3645ab8aeb","tid":1183221,"uid":51171,"like":21,"dislike":2,"scor